# BM klus BV — Core Rules

Full governance: `docs/governance/`

## Communication
- Respond to user in **Russian (RU)**
- All website content must be in **Dutch (nl-NL) only**
- Never write Russian or English text for public pages unless explicitly asked

## Hard bans (never do these)
- Never use hex colors in `className` — use design tokens (`text-primary`, `bg-card`, `border-border`). Exception: hero gradient `style={}`
- Never use Next.js `<Image>` — use `<ResponsiveImage baseName=... preset=... sizes=... alt=...>`
- Never import `buildSrcSet`, `getFallbackSrc`, or `image-manifest.json` in `"use client"` components — causes 47KB manifest leak
- Never create new routes without entry in `data/sitemap-plan.ts`
- Never fabricate prices, certifications, stats, or project counts — flag `[CLAIM_NEEDS_CONFIRMATION]`
- Never use npm or yarn — use `pnpm`
- `pnpm lint` will fail (ESLint not installed) — use `npx tsc --noEmit`
- Never output Dutch or Russian in the same sentence — pick one per context

